node.text:
Last weekend @thatlottheatre performed two sold-out performances of our #MILLENNIUMMEN Scratch Night. 
Images from #Showman #Boots #IncidentallyTonight 
Photos by @gabecphotography

Thank you to everyone that came and sorry we couldn't cram more of you into the theatre. We will be back! 
To have the opportunity to act, direct and see my writing on the stage for the first time was a beautiful honour and I am grateful to my fellow company men.

Thank you to the talented cast and crew for putting on an incredible show with some very special stories told!
